---
// Processo — cada mock simula a tela real daquela etapa.
---
<section class="sec processo" id="processo">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="kicker">Como trabalhamos</span>
      <h2>Um caminho curto e honesto.</h2>
      <p>Entender antes de codar, entregar em ciclos e melhorar com dado.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="zz">
      <!-- 01 Descoberta — tela de notas / briefing -->
      <div class="z">
        <div class="vis">
          <div class="mock">
            <div class="mock-bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i><span class="mock-title">briefing.md</span></div>
            <div class="mock-body scr-discovery">
              <span class="scr-h">Escopo do projeto</span>
              <div class="scr-checklist">
                <span class="ck done"><span class="box">✓</span> Entender o problema</span>
                <span class="ck done"><span class="box">✓</span> Mapear usuários</span>
                <span class="ck"><span class="box"></span> Definir MVP</span>
                <span class="ck"><span class="box"></span> Estimar prazo</span>
              </div>
              <div class="scr-note">
                <span class="scr-label">Anotações</span>
                <span class="scr-line ln-w8"></span>
                <span class="scr-line ln-w5"></span>
                <span class="scr-line ln-w7"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="txt">
          <span class="pill">Passo 01</span>
          <h3 class="zt">Descoberta</h3>
          <p class="zd">A gente senta com você pra entender a ideia, o problema e o que significa dar certo — antes de qualquer linha de código.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 02 Design — tela de wireframe / protótipo -->
      <div class="z">
        <div class="vis">
          <div class="mock">
            <div class="mock-bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i><span class="mock-title">prototipo.fig</span></div>
            <div class="mock-body scr-design">
              <div class="scr-sidebar">
                <span class="sb-block tall"></span>
                <span class="sb-block"></span>
                <span class="sb-block"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="scr-canvas">
                <span class="cv-header"></span>
                <div class="cv-cols">
                  <span class="cv-card"></span>
                  <span class="cv-card active"></span>
                  <span class="cv-card"></span>
                </div>
                <span class="cv-btn"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="txt">
          <span class="pill">Passo 02</span>
          <h3 class="zt">Design</h3>
          <p class="zd">Desenhamos e prototipamos cedo, pra você ajustar enquanto ainda é barato mudar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 03 Construção — editor de código -->
      <div class="z">
        <div class="vis">
          <div class="mock">
            <div class="mock-bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i><span class="mock-title">app.tsx</span></div>
            <div class="mock-body scr-code">
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">1</span><span class="c-key">import</span> <span class="c-str">createApp</span> <span class="c-key">from</span> <span class="c-str">'noven'</span></div>
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">2</span></div>
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">3</span><span class="c-key">const</span> app = <span class="c-fn">createApp</span>(</div>
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">4</span>  name: <span class="c-str">'seu-projeto'</span>,</div>
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">5</span>  <span class="c-fn">routes</span>: [<span class="c-str">'/dashboard'</span>],</div>
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">6</span>)</div>
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">7</span></div>
              <div class="code-ln"><span class="ln-n">8</span>app.<span class="c-fn">deploy</span>() <span class="c-cmt">{'// → produção'}</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="txt">
          <span class="pill">Passo 03</span>
          <h3 class="zt">Construção</h3>
          <p class="zd">Entregas curtas, contínuas e testadas: você vê o software crescer toda semana, sem surpresa no fim.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 04 No ar — dashboard com métricas -->
      <div class="z">
        <div class="vis">
          <div class="mock">
            <div class="mock-bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i><span class="mock-title">painel.noven.app</span></div>
            <div class="mock-body scr-dash">
              <div class="dash-row">
                <div class="dash-card">
                  <span class="dc-label">Uptime</span>
                  <span class="dc-value ok">99.8%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="dash-card">
                  <span class="dc-label">Usuários</span>
                  <span class="dc-value">1.247</span>
                </div>
                <div class="dash-card">
                  <span class="dc-label">Latência</span>
                  <span class="dc-value ok">42ms</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="dash-chart">
                <span class="chart-label">Requisições / semana</span>
                <div class="chart-bars">
                  <span class="cbar h40"></span>
                  <span class="cbar h55"></span>
                  <span class="cbar h45"></span>
                  <span class="cbar h70"></span>
                  <span class="cbar h60"></span>
                  <span class="cbar h85"></span>
                  <span class="cbar accent h92"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="txt">
          <span class="pill">Passo 04</span>
          <h3 class="zt">No ar & evolução</h3>
          <p class="zd">Colocamos no ar e seguimos por perto — medindo, ajustando e fazendo a solução acompanhar o seu negócio.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .zz { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
  .z { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; padding: 18px 0; }
  .z:nth-child(even) .vis { order: 2; }
  .vis .mock { aspect-ratio: 5 / 3; box-shadow: 0 18px 40px -24px rgba(0, 0, 0, .4); }
  .mock-title { margin-left: 10px; color: var(--soft); font-size: .72rem; font-family: var(--mono); }
  .txt .pill {
    display: inline-block; font-size: .74rem; color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 100px; padding: 3px 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .zt { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .zd { color: var(--muted); max-width: 46ch; }

  /* --- 01 Descoberta: briefing com checklist --- */
  .scr-discovery { gap: 12px; }
  .scr-h { font-weight: 700; font-size: .82rem; color: var(--ink); }
  .scr-checklist { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .ck { font-size: .76rem; color: var(--muted); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; }
  .ck .box {
    width: 15px; height: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1.5px solid var(--line);
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: .6rem; color: transparent; flex: none;
  }
  .ck.done .box { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); }
  .scr-note { margin-top: auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .scr-label { font-size: .65rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; color: var(--soft); }
  .scr-line { height: 7px; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--ink); opacity: .09; }
  .scr-line.ln-w8 { width: 85%; } .scr-line.ln-w5 { width: 50%; } .scr-line.ln-w7 { width: 70%; }

  /* --- 02 Design: wireframe com sidebar + canvas --- */
  .scr-design { flex-direction: row !important; gap: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; }
  .scr-sidebar {
    width: 22%; border-right: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 10px 8px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
  }
  .sb-block { height: 18px; border-radius: 5px; background: var(--ink); opacity: .07; }
  .sb-block.tall { height: 28px; }
  .scr-canvas { flex: 1; padding: 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .cv-header { height: 14px; width: 60%; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--ink); opacity: .10; }
  .cv-cols { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex: 1; }
  .cv-card {
    flex: 1; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px dashed var(--line);
    background: var(--surface); min-height: 40px;
  }
  .cv-card.active { border-color: var(--accent); border-style: solid; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--soft-accent); }
  .cv-btn { height: 16px; width: 35%; border-radius: 5px; background: var(--accent); opacity: .7; }

  /* --- 03 Construção: editor de código --- */
  .scr-code { gap: 2px !important; padding: 10px 0 10px 0 !important; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .7rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  .code-ln { display: flex; gap: 0; white-space: nowrap; padding: 0 12px; }
  .code-ln:hover { background: var(--soft-accent); }
  .ln-n { width: 20px; color: var(--soft); opacity: .5; flex: none; text-align: right; margin-right: 12px; user-select: none; }
  .c-key { color: var(--accent); }
  .c-str { color: var(--muted); }
  .c-fn { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
  .c-cmt { color: var(--soft); opacity: .6; }

  /* --- 04 Dashboard: métricas + gráfico --- */
  .scr-dash { gap: 10px !important; }
  .dash-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .dash-card {
    flex: 1; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px;
  }
  .dc-label { font-size: .6rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; color: var(--soft); }
  .dc-value { font-weight: 700; font-size: .92rem; letter-spacing: -.02em; color: var(--ink); }
  .dc-value.ok { color: var(--accent); }
  .dash-chart {
    flex: 1; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .chart-label { font-size: .6rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; color: var(--soft); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .chart-bars { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 6px; flex: 1; }
  .cbar { flex: 1; background: var(--ink); opacity: .12; border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0; min-height: 4px; }
  .cbar.accent { background: var(--accent); opacity: .8; }
  .h40 { height: 40%; } .h45 { height: 45%; } .h55 { height: 55%; }
  .h60 { height: 60%; } .h70 { height: 70%; } .h85 { height: 85%; } .h92 { height: 92%; }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .z { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; padding: 14px 0; }
    .z:nth-child(even) .vis { order: 0; }
    .scr-code { font-size: .62rem; }
  }
</style>
